data.description: Come check out this charming 5 bed, 2.5 bath home in the heart of Dacula. Main level features hardwood floors, spacious kitchen, fresh paint, and stainless steel appliances. TANKLESS water heater, Walk in closet in large master bedroom, complete with its own separate AC system. .  Basement includes updated bathroom, bedroom, and large family room. There is flex space perfect for home office, gym, or extra storage. Basement area also has workshop space.  Enjoy your evenings out back on the sprawling, covered deck.  Backyard features privacy fence, chicken coop, large outbuilding, garden area, and blueberry bushes.  Septic tank pumped in April.  Desirable school system. No HOA!  So bring your family, chickens, berry baskets, and tomato plants and make this home your own!
